276
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] Iz dva razloga, naravno. Jedan je taj što ideološki.

277
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] Kad kažem ideološki, mislim na to da, recimo,

278
00:36:16,860 --> 00:36:22,400
