335
00:40:56,699 --> 00:40:59,500
[SPEAKER_01] Niko, ne, nitko. To je stvar.

336
00:40:59,500 --> 00:41:03,219
[SPEAKER_00] Eto. I svega što ste navrojali.

337
00:41:03,219 --> 00:41:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, propitan koliko je Trump zainteresiran za mir, a koliko je zainteresiran za približavanje Rusiji.

338
00:41:08,539 --> 00:41:18,820
