363
00:43:31,619 --> 00:43:37,699
[SPEAKER_01] kad su svi rekli, gotovo je on pušta Ukrajinu, on radi dogovor sa Rusima.

364
00:43:37,699 --> 00:43:39,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, on radi dogovor s jednim i s drugima.

365
00:43:39,920 --> 00:43:41,679
[SPEAKER_01] On je biznismen.

366
00:43:41,679 --> 00:43:42,460
[SPEAKER_01] On je biznismen.

367
00:43:42,460 --> 00:43:46,019
[SPEAKER_01] Pitanje je što njemu Rusi mogu ponuditi.

368
00:43:46,019 --> 00:43:47,780
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, znamo za Ukraince.

369
00:43:47,780 --> 00:43:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ukrajinci su mu nudili minerale.

370
00:43:50,000 --> 00:43:52,659
